//TEXT
<jaT0001>I leapt for cover behind the fire door, and waited for the order from the control room to start closing the door.
<enT0001>I leapt for cover behind the fire door, and waited for the order from the control room to start closing the door.

//TEXT
<jaT0002>However...
<enT0002>However...

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0003>"It's not working! The device to close the door isn't moving!"
<enT0003>"It's not working! The device to close the door isn't moving!"

//TEXT
<jaT0004>The shock from Cellaria-san's painful words nearly caused me to faint.
<enT0004>The shock from Cellaria-san's painful words nearly caused me to faint.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0005>"Wh-why?!"
<enT0005>"Wh-why?!"

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0006>"They could have made a mistake, or the door itself could be broken. I don't know the cause. But there's no sign of it working."
<enT0006>"They could have made a mistake, or the door itself could be broken. I don't know the cause. But there's no sign of it working."

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0007>"......"
<enT0007>"......"

//TEXT
<jaT0008>I recalled what Nao had said about the control room. "It's not going that well". I see. So they couldn't fix it.
<enT0008>I recalled what Nao had said about the control room. "It's not going that well". I see. So they couldn't fix it.

//TEXT
<jaT0009>If it was going to end like this, I should have left someone more skilled with computers in the control room. I grinded my teeth at my own poor judgement, but it was already too late!
<enT0009>If it was going to end like this, I should have left someone more skilled with computers in the control room. I grinded my teeth at my own poor judgement, but it was already too late!

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0010>"Dammit! Hey, Kazuhiko!"
<enT0010>"Dammit! Hey, Kazuhiko!"

//TEXT
<jaT0011>I called out to the signaler who wasn't doing anything anymore.
<enT0011>I called out to the signaler who wasn't doing anything anymore.

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0012>"Y-yes, What is it?"
<enT0012>"Y-yes, What is it?"

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0013>"Get back to the control room, now! Do whatever you can to shut all the emergency doors, including this one. Cellaria-san and I will stay here and hold them off."
<enT0013>"Get back to the control room, now! Do whatever you can to shut all the emergency doors, including this one. Cellaria-san and I will stay here and hold them off."

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0014>"Eh? But then?!"
<enT0014>"Eh? But then?!"

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0015>"Just go!!"
<enT0015>"Just go!!"

//TEXT 【Kazuhiko】
<jaT0016>"Alright!"
<enT0016>"Alright!"

//TEXT
<jaT0017>Startled by my threatening tone, Kazuhiko ran off to the secondary control room with no further objections.
<enT0017>Startled by my threatening tone, Kazuhiko ran off to the secondary control room with no further objections.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0018>"Cellaria-san."
<enT0018>"Cellaria-san."

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0019>"I know. Let's do as much as we can."
<enT0019>"I know. Let's do as much as we can."

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0020>"I'm sorry for getting you into this..."
<enT0020>"I'm sorry for getting you into this..."

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0021>"It's nothing to be ashamed of. All you did was choose the best option you could, Shuhei-san."
<enT0021>"It's nothing to be ashamed of. All you did was choose the best option you could, Shuhei-san."

//TEXT
<jaT0022>As Cellaria-san spoke, she raised her gun and looked down the passage into the Hamal. There were over 10 people. Each armed with a sub-machine gun.
<enT0022>As Cellaria-san spoke, she raised her gun and looked down the passage into the Hamal. There were over 10 people. Each armed with a sub-machine gun.

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0023>"Looks like we're out of time..."
<enT0023>"Looks like we're out of time..."

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0024>"I'll go first. Cellaria-san, you fall back and cover me."
<enT0024>"I'll go first. Cellaria-san, you fall back and cover me."

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0025>"Eh? Th-then?"
<enT0025>"Eh? Th-then?"

//TEXT
<jaT0026>As Cellaria-san tried to say something, she noticed my expression, and swallowed her next line.
<enT0026>As Cellaria-san tried to say something, she noticed my expression, and swallowed her next line.

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0027>"Understood. I'll cover you as best as I can."
<enT0027>"Understood. I'll cover you as best as I can."

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0028>"Hahaha..."
<enT0028>"Hahaha..."

//TEXT
<jaT0029>With a self derisive laugh, I leapt out with my gun aimed at the enemy. They were already upon us, and I had to stop them from entering.
<enT0029>With a self derisive laugh, I leapt out with my gun aimed at the enemy. They were already upon us, and I had to stop them from entering.

//TEXT
<jaT0030>......
<enT0030>......

//TEXT
<jaT0031>I saw Nao's lonely face before my consciousness was quickly buried in darkness.
<enT0031>I saw Nao's lonely face before my consciousness was quickly buried in darkness.

